.DT
set_list_function
Disk World creator help
set_list_function

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_list_function -  This method sets the function to use when listing something from the shop.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_list_function(function func)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^func%^RESET%^ - the function to set
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/inherit/item_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the function to use when listing something from
the shop.  The function will be called with two arguements, the
first is the player, the second is the array of objects being
bought.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_list_function(), set_buy_function(), set_browse_function(), query_list_function()

.EP

